### 测试锁，设置 count
GET http://{{host}}/.well-known/test/lock/set-count?value=1

### 测试锁，减少 count，同步（在同步路由方法中调用），不加锁
GET http://{{host}}/.well-known/test/lock/decrease-count
# ab.exe -n 10 -c 10 http://127.0.0.1:8000/.well-known/test/lock/decrease-count

### 测试锁，减少 count，同步（在异步路由方法中调用），不加锁
GET http://{{host}}/.well-known/test/lock/async-decrease-count
# ab.exe -n 10 -c 10 http://127.0.0.1:8000/.well-known/test/lock/async-decrease-count

### 测试锁，减少 count，异步，不加锁
GET http://{{host}}/.well-known/test/lock/decrease-count-async
# ab.exe -n 10 -c 10 http://127.0.0.1:8000/.well-known/test/lock/decrease-count-async

### 测试锁，减少 count，异步，加锁
GET http://{{host}}/.well-known/test/lock/decrease-count-with-lock
# ab.exe -n 10 -c 10 http://127.0.0.1:8000/.well-known/test/lock/decrease-count-with-lock

